## 6. `sales_orders.csv` — Sales Orders

**Description:** Domestic and export sales orders linked back to the production run that fulfilled them.

**Grain:** One row per order line.
**Primary key:** `order_id`
**Foreign key:** `run_id` → `production_runs.run_id`

| Column | Type | Nullable | Description | Example | Notes |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| `order_id` | String | No | Unique sales order identifier | `SO-0000001` | Zero-padded sequence. |
| `order_date` | Date | No | When the order was placed | `2025-09-12` | Run date + 1–60 day shipping lag. |
| `customer` | String | No | Buying customer | `WinMart`, `Whole Foods Market` | Domestic uses real VN retailer names; export uses Faker company names. |
| `country` | String | No | Destination country | `Vietnam`, `Germany`, `United States` | 1 domestic + 15 export countries. |
| `region` | String | No | Geographic region | `Domestic`, `Europe`, `North America`, `Asia-Pacific`, `Middle East` | Roll-up for region-level analysis. |
| `channel` | String | No | Sales channel | `Modern Trade`, `HORECA`, `Wholesale` | Domestic and export use different channel sets. |
| `is_domestic` | Boolean | No | Domestic Vietnam vs export | `True`, `False` | ~55% domestic / 45% export. |
| `is_organic` | Boolean | No | Whether the SKU sold is organic | `True`, `False` | Higher share in export. |
| `run_id` | String | No | Production run that fulfilled this order | `RUN-000123` | FK to `production_runs`. Enables full traceability. |
| `product` | String | No | Cocoxim SKU sold | `Cocoxim Organic Coconut Water 330ml` | Same naming as `production_runs.product`. |
| `quantity_units` | Integer | No | Units in the order | `45000` | Wholesale orders much larger than retail. |
| `unit_price_usd` | Float | No | Price per unit in USD (FOB) | `0.385` | After ±8% market variance. |
| `revenue_usd` | Float | No | quantity × unit_price_usd | `17325.00` | Normalized currency for global comparisons. |
| `revenue_local` | Float | No | Revenue in the destination's currency | `17325.00` (USD) or `424,462,500` (VND) | Use `currency` to interpret. |
| `currency` | String | No | ISO currency code of `revenue_local` | `USD`, `EUR`, `VND` | VND for domestic, EUR for Eurozone, USD elsewhere. |
| `margin_pct` | Float | No | Margin percentage | `27.4` | Organic averages 28%, conventional 20%. |
| `margin_usd` | Float | No | Absolute margin contribution | `4747.05` | revenue_usd × margin_pct / 100. |
| `on_time_delivery` | Boolean | No | Whether the order shipped on time | `True`, `False` | ~92% on-time overall, 88% for organic (extra cert checks). |

**Business notes**

- The `run_id` foreign key is what makes lot-level traceability possible end-to-end: from a single bottle in a German supermarket back to the smallholder farmer in Mo Cay Nam.
- Use `revenue_usd` for cross-country comparisons; `revenue_local` for in-country reporting.
- `margin_pct` is a key strategic KPI — used to justify the organic premium.

