## Suggested Certified Measures (DAX)

| Measure | Formula | Format |
|---|---|---|
| **Yield %** | `SUM(production_runs[actual_yield]) / SUM(production_runs[expected_yield])` | Percentage |
| **Grade A %** | `COUNTROWS(FILTER(lots, lots[grade]="A")) / COUNTROWS(lots)` | Percentage |
| **Average Brix** | `AVERAGE(lots[brix])` | Decimal (2) |
| **Yield Loss (L)** | `SUM(production_runs[expected_yield]) - SUM(production_runs[actual_yield])` | Decimal |
| **Total Revenue USD** | `SUM(sales_orders[revenue_usd])` | Currency |
| **Total Margin USD** | `SUM(sales_orders[margin_usd])` | Currency |
| **Margin %** | `[Total Margin USD] / [Total Revenue USD]` | Percentage |
| **On-Time Delivery %** | `AVERAGE(sales_orders[on_time_delivery] = TRUE)` | Percentage |
| **QA Pass Rate** | `COUNTROWS(FILTER(quality_tests, quality_tests[pass_fail]="Pass")) / COUNTROWS(quality_tests)` | Percentage |
| **Organic Revenue %** | `[Organic Revenue] / [Total Revenue USD]` | Percentage |
| **Lots per Run (avg)** | `AVERAGE(production_runs[num_lots_consumed])` | Whole number |

